Program: Outlook
Title: Domestic Violence in Malawi
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbs81
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
New law to reduce domestic violence in Malawi, interview with a campaigner for the law who suffered from beatings by her husband. Also, an interview with Aki Ra, a former child soldier from Cambodia who is now involved with clearing mines. Part two of Thembi Ngubane diary on living with HIV in South Africa. Show less